General information
===================

Yage is an open-source game engine based on OpenGL


Getting latest source code
==========================

HTTP: git clone https://github.com/santa01/yage.git
GIT:  git clone git://github.com/santa01/yage.git


Package dependencies
====================

* X11 shared libraries
* XrandR shared libraries
* OpenGL shared libraries (usually priovided with your graphics card driver)


Building
========

See INSTALL for details


Troubleshooting
===============

Report all bugs, feature requests and TODO's here:
  <https://github.com/santa01/yage/issues>


